{
  "id": "RAW_da3bee3e",
  "title": "千问 APP 悄悄上线，阿里的 AI 超级入口也终于来了。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647676804&idx=1&sn=7a05a038efa2456b247023f90e040e7d",
  "date": "2025-11-17 02:34:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">昨天，阿里的千问APP，在应用商店里。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">终于悄悄上线了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500193090\" data-ratio=\"1.0240740740740741\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5ca0bc2a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURokR2C2HXIEzgb8XGEvzCUFiaRHwQzEDTyD3PursHicI2c5A9uIbL25Gd28QOJMTKrLc0Ciay4dibkTzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">打开以后，就是一个非常简洁的颜色。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从之前的通义APP的双色渐变，变成了现在的属于千问的单色。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500193091\" data-ratio=\"1.0231481481481481\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=22e07fd9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURokR2C2HXIEzgb8XGEvzCUFUzqOibLTaSCSu8WWTYtnqibA569LBH5YgU5UGibN38sBSmibOrFDdUoxsA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">功能增加了很多，模型也支持了Qwen全系列最新模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">界面变得比以前简约了不少。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个事非常有意思，我觉得非常的值得来聊一下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">我感觉阿里，好像找到了一种非常行之有效的打法，就是品牌的迭代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">前几天轰轰烈烈的饿了么改名淘宝闪购的事，互联网圈大家肯定都知道了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">表面上看，好像就是把几个字从A换成B。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"345\" data-backw=\"530\" data-imgfileid=\"500193105\" data-ratio=\"0.6509433962264151\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"530\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b8361040&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURokR2C2HXIEzgb8XGEvzCUFIicgDLia9m9IWqUd6VFbDKFtwc13Z3fhNlXq9VWFfsLaDFjaTfZCZJlw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但从品牌角度来说，这个决策极度的激进，但，确实把整个阿里的即时零售盘活了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在反过来看AI这边。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其实非常坦诚的讲，阿里的AI，在全世界，都是首屈一指的，更有模型圈的源神之名。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Qwen 系列的开源模型，已经在全球开源圈混成了一种公共基础设施的感觉，我相信所有做开发的人，提起Qwen，多数嘴角是上扬的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.38333333333333336\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dbd430d2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqH1OjjYzYJ6MkNVJiaxZqZ3zOYhWAfPG0435q0x5QJmSurLVqWRibDmeYel9Bs42bRTxMuozohF2Ag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D18\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">基本就是吊打全世界。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3703703703703705\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d388d85f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURqH1OjjYzYJ6MkNVJiaxZqZ3ERNa5QQmtiau64qlwbUBWufVLc8b0frHMz9ErA0ltuE6c7iaiahly4BOA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D17\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但如果你细细的看一下，你就会发现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所有模型的名字，都叫Qwen。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">中文名，就是千问。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Qwen3-Max、Qwen3-VL、Qwen3-Omini等等等等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而另一条线，偏艺术和视觉的，则叫Wan，也就是，万相。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我写过的Wan2.2-Animate。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但问题来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">普通用户并不生活在Hugging Face上，也不生活在Github上，普通用户生活在手机APP上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为大家并不理解，千问和通义APP，是什么关系？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，这个名字，被正式定义成千问APP的那一刻，我的第一反应，其实是有一些开心，他们，终于觉得到这个时间点了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">做了一个非常简单，但又非常关键的事情：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">把模型和产品的名字，拉回到了一条线上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">千问，不再只是HuggingFace里的模型、云上 API 的一个名字。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">千问，变成了你能装在手机里的那个App，变成了用户天天点的那个入口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">从这一刻起，开发者和普通用户，第一次有机会在同一个词下面对话。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">大家慢慢开始意识到，AI 时代更稀缺的是两样东西：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一是注意力的入口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">二是完整的、连续的、高质量数据。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">入口越少，数据越集中，AI 越有空间发挥。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">淘宝闪购做的是，把本地生活的场景，合并回淘宝。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">千问做的，则有点像是把阿里系分散各处的AI触点，重新收束到一个品牌上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一切统统归为一句话：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">有事找千问。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">让注意力，极致的集中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">同时，这次的千问APP，也重回了极简。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">并且，可以直接切换到Qwen3-Max模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500193093\" data-ratio=\"0.48148148148148145\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e4eeb11e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURokR2C2HXIEzgb8XGEvzCUFJs6URLNEHibOFT7CVEnicSKQa7C3qJPf9s1VVZkFxiaJpZiazj2FH4vLQw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">如果我没记错的话，这是普通用户，第一次可以在官方APP上，使用阿里的这个系列里面最强的Qwen3模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">而且不是纯粹的裸模，是跟ChatGPT那种一样，上面包了一层系统Prompt，对普通用户来说，体验会更加的友好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">比如，我让他写个比较有文采的话。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">“奥本海默在按下原子弹试爆按钮的那一刻，心里在想什么？设身处地站在奥本海默的角度，以他的口吻，为他写一封倾诉矛盾内心的自白信。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500193094\" data-ratio=\"1.025\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cdbf32c3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURokR2C2HXIEzgb8XGEvzCUF81aeaUbSUaej4OyT1lhgIBR612n0AawZ2WXor8nZXTBeZ2etNEtacw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">大家可以看看千问的文笔。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">说实话，我写了这么多的内容，在我看来，千问的文笔，是国内首屈一当的了，可能跟现在的GPT-5.1-Thinking在人味上相比，还有一点小小的差距，但是，也已经是非常非常好的了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">特别是那最后一句：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">“于长夜未尽之时”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">喜欢。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">并且同样的也是为C端用户做考虑，所以，其实你会发现，搜索是默认打开的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500193096\" data-ratio=\"0.34814814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=04c37a80&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURokR2C2HXIEzgb8XGEvzCUFCEQZXIvVWEBVGf7MgYEibJ0vZ8P5UkyHFSw99hSAriaicsELjuB7ibblibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我问：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">千问会直接先以最快的速度联网搜索以后，再给出答案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500193097\" data-ratio=\"1.0212962962962964\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a550afca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURokR2C2HXIEzgb8XGEvzCUFIFmp3WiaZLTEBF5gvicx7H3gsMiaB13tibCpNPFG4IlXnKzliccFlOqJhkw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很久以前我不理解，说为什么C端的AI产品要么干。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">为什么不是提供一个选择，问是否打开联网搜索，让用户自己判断。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">后来，想明白了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">特别DeepSeek那段时间所带来的幻觉问题，你会发现，普通用户很多时候，并不会理解一个大模型，为什么不能回答昨天的热点事件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">什么叫模型的知识是固定的？什么叫知识是有截止时间的？为啥还要开个联网搜索？为啥我关了就在这瞎答了？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">毕竟，纯大模型离线回答，肯定会胡说八道，尤其是新闻、时事、产品价格、活动、政策等等，各种关于今年、最近、现在的问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">普通用户也不会说原来是我忘记开联网搜索了，这就是你当初的产品做的不行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以啊，C端的APP级别产品，本身就是强调短平快，默认开启搜索，真的省心省力，我自己用ChatGPT也是，经常问个问题，发现忘记开联网了，然后又停止，打开，重问。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">C端产品，体验都在细节之间。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除了传统的大模型问答之外，千问这次也是一个大一统的The One产品。</span></span>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">把Wan2.5、Iamge Edit、Omni啥的，全部都接进去了。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在下方，以一个一个的面向用户的场景功能做了展示。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500193098\" data-ratio=\"0.3861111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=77711e77&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURokR2C2HXIEzgb8XGEvzCUFCaJwxe59NheG8Jq63wrqqb68qHTdkGR3MbWWvrWXictJUpSPOMqw09w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">功能非常多，但是其实你也不用都把他们背下来或者干啥。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为千问这次做了很强的意图识别和路由。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以一个对话框内，基本就全部都能完成。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就像在画图上，你也不用真的去找到那个AI修图的按钮，你可以直接传一张图上去，用嘴P图。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如，我扔了一个我超级爱喝的外星人电解质水，我就可以把这张图传上去，让它给我改成，卡兹克电解质水。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500193101\" data-ratio=\"1.375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cb641b34&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURokR2C2HXIEzgb8XGEvzCUFcGWQdk7Sz0QrXntRPRHZGdd28NDexWRZZicyCs9JcBR0keD3Pia5HW2A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">即使是这么歪七八糟的图，依然改字改的很好。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有前段时间很火的AI三宫格图。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">千问也可以直接画。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0212962962962964\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500193099\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=15dfb7b4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURokR2C2HXIEzgb8XGEvzCUFdwZLYiaQib2qhpXImL66llq2ncFPFLYdiaNYgUaSxsJUicj41mkHR6lKGQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">唯一有点瑕疵的就是，字一多，确实中文字还是会有点不稳。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除了画图。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你也可以直接在对话框里，传张图，让千问帮你把答案都填上。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"500193100\" data-ratio=\"1.5314814814814814\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b99faa97&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURokR2C2HXIEzgb8XGEvzCUFzgRGILbDe2M7m2s1w77PpYBVrtY3D5dzKQiccqw6zovSsUpbR4kvDhQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其他的，视频通话、实时记录、翻译、AI生视频啥的基本上也都应有尽有。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而现在，这些，都属于千问。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最屌的模型叫千问。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个超级APP，也叫千问。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"3930\" data-end=\"3953\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这些，共同构成了，属于这个叫做千问的品牌。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"3955\" data-end=\"4042\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">没有品牌，技术会以一种混乱的方式浮现在世界上，比如充满名词、缩写、架构图、版本号、参数量。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"3955\" data-end=\"4042\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这些东西对你我这种盯着行业的人来说很迷人，但对绝大多数的普通用户来说，只是一团听不太懂的虚无。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"4044\" data-end=\"4085\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有了品牌，技术才有可能，被压缩成一句话，一个 Logo，一种视觉，一种语气。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"4087\" data-end=\"4132\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所有复杂的东西，被折叠进这一个词里。当你点击它的时候，那些复杂性才在后台一点点展开。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5031\" data-end=\"5075\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当阿里把饿了么藏进淘宝，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">把Qwen装进千问。。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"4087\" data-end=\"4132\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">技术，是让你可以发出声音。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"4087\" data-end=\"4132\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">而品牌，是让别人愿意记住那句话。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"4087\" data-end=\"4132\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对公司是这样，对人也是这样。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5127\" data-end=\"5197\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你可以不关心品牌，但品牌从来没有放过你。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5127\" data-end=\"5197\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你每天发的东西、你写的每一篇文章、你转发的每一个链接，都在悄悄地，替你给世界写一行说明：</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5199\" data-end=\"5213\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">这个人，大概是干什么的。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5199\" data-end=\"5213\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这就是你自己的品牌。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5215\" data-end=\"5292\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI会继续变强，模型会一代又一代地迭代。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5215\" data-end=\"5292\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Qwen会从3变成4，从4变成5，千问APP也将成为所有普通用户接触模这些最新的模型的首选。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5294\" data-end=\"5321\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而我觉得在这个过程中，我们可能，也该给自己起一个更准确的名字。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5323\" data-end=\"5373\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">是那种在我们脑子里，在我们晚上躺在床上，问自己那句最俗气的问题：</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5375\" data-end=\"5384\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">我到底，是谁？</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5386\" data-end=\"5458\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也许，等哪天我们能把这句话回答得足够清楚，就会突然发现，所谓技术也好，品牌也好，不过都是你和这个时代谈判时，手里捏着的两张牌。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5460\" data-end=\"5483\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">阿里现在开始认真打这两张牌了。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5460\" data-end=\"5483\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这两张牌，都很重要。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"5460\" data-end=\"5483\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那接下来，下一个是谁呢？</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style:solid;text-decoration-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">wzglyay@virxact.com</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "阿里“千问 APP”正式上线，将底层 Qwen 模型与用户产品品牌统一，旨在集中 AI 用户入口和数据，优化 C 端体验。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "阿里“千问 APP”正式上线，将底层 Qwen 模型与用户产品品牌统一，旨在集中 AI 用户入口和数据，优化 C 端体验。",
  "summary": "文章报道了阿里巴巴“千问 APP”的悄然上线，强调这是阿里在 AI 领域的一次重要品牌和产品策略调整。作者以“饿了么改名淘宝闪购”为例，指出阿里在进行激进的品牌迭代以盘活业务。通过将强大的 Qwen 系列模型（包括 Qwen3-Max）与用户端 APP 统一命名为“千问”，阿里旨在消除开发者与普通用户之间的认知隔阂，集中用户注意力，并聚合高质量数据。新版 APP 界面更简洁，默认开启联网搜索以避免 AI“幻觉”，并集成了多模态功能（如 AI 修图、绘图），致力于打造一个“大一统”的 AI 超级入口。作者认为，在 AI 时代，品牌建设与技术本身同样重要，它能将复杂技术转化为用户易于理解和记忆的价值。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "阿里通过“千问 APP”统一 AI 产品与模型品牌，旨在集中用户注意力和数据。",
      "explanation": "将底层模型（Qwen）与用户端产品（千问 APP）命名一致，降低用户理解门槛，形成清晰的 AI 入口，实现注意力与数据的聚合，推动 AI 普惠应用。"
    },
    {
      "point": "千问 APP 集成了 Qwen 全系列最新模型，并优化了 C 端用户体验。",
      "explanation": "首次向普通用户开放 Qwen3-Max 模型，并默认开启联网搜索、整合多模态功能，提升了应用的实用性和易用性，减少用户操作负担，解决大模型常见痛点。"
    },
    {
      "point": "品牌在 AI 时代的重要性日益凸显，将复杂技术转化为用户可感知的价值。",
      "explanation": "品牌能将复杂的 AI 技术抽象为简洁的形象和口号，帮助用户理解和记住产品，是技术与市场沟通的关键桥梁，也是企业竞争力的重要组成部分。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "千问，不再只是 HuggingFace 里的模型、云上 API 的一个名字。千问，变成了你能装在手机里的那个 App，变成了用户天天点的那个入口。",
    "从这一刻起，开发者和普通用户，第一次有机会在同一个词下面对话。",
    "入口越少，数据越集中，AI 越有空间发挥。",
    "C 端的 APP 级别产品，本身就是强调短平快，默认开启搜索，真的省心省力。",
    "没有品牌，技术会以一种混乱的方式浮现在世界上... 有了品牌，技术才有可能，被压缩成一句话，一个 Logo，一种视觉，一种语气。"
  ],
